@0    = ~Animate Dead
(Necromancy) 

Level: 4
Range: 10 yards 
Duration: 8 hours 
Casting Time: 1 round
Area of Effect: Special 
Saving Throw: None 

This spell creates the lowest of the undead monsters, skeletons and zombies, from the remains of dead humans, demihumans or humanoids.  Once animated, the undead stay around until they are destroyed in combat, a powerful priest or paladin succesfully turns them, or eight hours pass, in which case they will crumble to dust.  The animating magic cannot be dispelled.

Casting this spell is not a good act and only evil wizards use it frequently.  Good or neutral wizards using this spell risk attracting the attention of dark powers or face alignment shifts.~
