Range: 10 yards 
Duration: 8 hours 
Casting Time: 1 round
Area of Effect: Special 
Saving Throw: None 

Through this powerful necromantic ritual the necromancer animates the skeletal remains of soldiers slain in battle as a small squad of powerful skeleton warriors.  The spell animates two skeleton warriors at level 14, four at level 21 and finally six at level 28.

Casting this spell is not a good act and only evil wizards use it frequently.  Neutral wizards using this spell risk attracting the attention of dark powers or face alignment shifts.~


